line_1: Here maids of fifty, widows of fourscore,
line_2: May all get marri'd for a penny more.

line_1: And steps from four-and-twenty to fourscore.
line_2: Runs in a moment all his stages o'er,

line_1: "Of long miles at the least 'twould have sav'd us fourscore.
line_2: "I wish I had read this same bible before:
